\x09-fi fifo_name, wlan fifo path name

\x09-mode val, 1: ap unconfigured, 2: client unconfigured (enrollee),

\x09-gen-pin, generate pin code for local entitiy
\x09-peer_pin, assign pin code for peer entitiy
\x09-local_pin, assign pin code for local device
\x09-sig_start, start wsc protocol
\x09-sig_pbc, signal PBC mode
\x09-start_pbc, start PBC mode
\x09-daemon, run as daemon
